			<h1 class="project-hero__title">Can California put cars in the rear-view mirror?</h1>

			
						<p class="project-hero__intro">Lawmakers are nudging motorists into ride-sharing, public transit and housing that enables both.</p>
			
							<div class="project-hero__caption">

											<svg role="img" class="icon icon--camera" aria-label="camera"><use xlink:href="https://calmatters.org/wp-content/themes/thenewsproject/dist/svg/dist/symbol/svg/sprite.symbol.svg#camera"></use></svg>						<span>Quintessential California: a convertible on Highway 1 along the Big Sur coastline. Photo by Pgiam/istockphotos.com</span>
									</div>
